                    </a>
                </h3>
                                        <ul class="column__cards is--featured">
                                                                                                                        <li>
                        <a href="https://www-develop.yogananda.org/it/blog/un-messaggio-di-brother-chidananda-sulla-guerra-in-ucraina" title="Un messaggio di Brother Chidananda sulla guerra in Ucraina" id="nav_blog_chd_message_war_Ukraine_click">
                                                            <div class="image uprise">
                                    <img src="https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/yogananda-dev/CHD-1803_43-01_Chidananda_2.jpg" alt="">
                                </div>
